   346→  [#2807](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2807)
   347→- Fixed ID collisions when the numeric suffix gets used.
   348→  [#2846](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2846)
   349→- Fixed missing css vars for no-js dark mode.
   350→  [#2850](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2850)
   352→## mdBook 0.4.52
   353→[v0.4.51...v0.4.52](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/compare/v0.4.51...v0.4.52)
   357→### Added
   358→- Added the ability to redirect `#` HTML fragments using the existing `output.html.redirect` table.
   359→  [#2747](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2747)
   360→- Added the `rel="edit"` attribute to the edit page button.
   361→  [#2702](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2702)
   363→### Changed
   364→- The search index is now only loaded when the search input is opened instead of always being loaded.
   365→  [#2553](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2553)
   366→  [#2735](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2735)
   367→- The `mdbook serve` command has switched its underlying server library from warp to axum.
   368→  [#2748](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2748)
   369→- Updated dependencies.
   370→  [#2752](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2752)
   372→### Fixed
   373→- The sidebar is now set to `display:none` when it is hidden in order to prevent the browser's search from thinking the sidebar's text is visible.
   374→  [#2725](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2725)
   375→- Fixed search index URL not updating correctly when `hash-files` is enabled.
   376→  [#2742](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2742)
   377→  [#2746](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2746)
   378→- Fixed several sidebar animation bugs, particularly when manually resizing.
   379→  [#2750](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2750)
   381→## mdBook 0.4.51
   382→[v0.4.50...v0.4.51](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/compare/v0.4.50...v0.4.51)
   384→### Fixed
