   386→  [#2713](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2713)
   388→## mdBook 0.4.50
   389→[v0.4.49...v0.4.50](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/compare/v0.4.49...v0.4.50)
   391→### Added
   392→
