   416→## mdBook 0.4.49
   417→[v0.4.48...v0.4.49](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/compare/v0.4.48...v0.4.49)
   419→### Added
   420→
   421→- Added a warning on unused fields in the root of `book.toml`.
