   424→### Changed
   425→
   426→- Updated dependencies.
   427→  [#2650](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2650)
   428→  [#2688](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2688)
   429→- Updated minimum Rust version to 1.81.
   430→  [#2688](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2688)
   431→- The unused `book.multilingual` field is no longer serialized, or shown in `mdbook init`.
   432→  [#2689](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2689)
   433→- Speed up search index loading by using `JSON.parse` instead of parsing JavaScript.
   434→  [#2633](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2633)
   436→### Fixed
   437→
   438→- Search highlighting will not try to highlight in SVG `<text>` elements because it breaks the element.
   439→  [#2668](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2668)
   440→- Fixed scrolling of the sidebar when a search highlight term is in the URL.
   441→  [#2675](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2675)
   442→- Fixed issues when multiple footnote definitions use the same ID. Now, only one definition is used, and a warning is displayed.
   443→  [#2681](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2681)
   444→- The sidebar is now restricted to 80% of the viewport width to make it possible to collapse it when the viewport is very narrow.
   445→  [#2679](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2679)
   447→## mdBook 0.4.48
   448→[v0.4.47...v0.4.48](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/compare/v0.4.47...v0.4.48)
   450→### Added
   451→
   452→- Footnotes now have back-reference links. These links bring the reader back to the original location. As part of this change, footnotes are now only rendered at the bottom of the page. This also includes some styling updates and fixes for footnote rendering.
   453→  [#2626](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2626)
   454→- Added an "Auto" theme selection option which will default to the system-preferred mode. This will also automatically switch when the system changes the preferred mode.
   455→  [#2576](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2576)
   457→### Changed
   458→
   459→- The `searchindex.json` file has been removed; only the `searchindex.js` file will be generated.
