   461→- Updated Javascript code to use eslint.
   462→  [#2554](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2554)
   463→- An error is generated if there are duplicate files in `SUMMARY.md`.
   464→  [#2613](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2613)
