   594→  [#2388](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2388)
   596→## mdBook 0.4.39
   597→[v0.4.38...v0.4.39](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/compare/v0.4.38...v0.4.39)
   599→### Fixed
   600→
   601→- Fixed the automatic deploy broken in the previous release.
   602→  [#2383](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2383)
   604→## mdBook 0.4.38
   605→[v0.4.37...v0.4.38](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/compare/v0.4.37...v0.4.38)
   607→### Added
   608→
   609→- Added `nix` to the default set of languages supported for syntax highlighting.
   610→  [#2262](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2262)
   612→### Changed
   613→
   614→- The `output.html.curly-quotes` option has been renamed to `output.html.smart-punctuation` to better reflect what it does. The old option `curly-quotes` is kept for compatibility, but may be removed in the future.
   615→  [#2327](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2327)
   616→- The file-watcher used in `mdbook serve` and `mdbook watch` now uses a poll-based watcher instead of the native operating system notifications. This should fix issues on various systems and environments, and more accurately detect when files change. The native watcher can still be used with the `--watcher native` CLI option.
   617→  [#2325](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2325)
   618→- `mdbook test` output now includes color, and shows relative paths to the source.
   619→  [#2259](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2259)
   620→- Updated dependencies, MSRV raised to 1.74
   621→  [#2350](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2350)
   622→  [#2351](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2351)
   623→  [#2378](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2378)
   624→  [#2381](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2381)
   626→### Fixed
   627→
   628→- Reduced memory allocation when copying files.
   629→  [#2355](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2355)
   630→- Fixed the horizontal divider in `SUMMARY.md` from being indented into the previous nested section.
   631→  [#2364](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2364)
   632→- Removed unnecessary `@import` in the CSS.
   633→  [#2260](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2260)
   635→## mdBook 0.4.37
   636→[v0.4.36...v0.4.37](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/compare/v0.4.36...v0.4.37)
   638→### Changed
   639→- ❗️ Updated the markdown parser. This brings in many changes to more closely follow the CommonMark spec. This may cause some small rendering changes. It is recommended to compare the output of the old and new version to check for changes. See <https://github.com/raphlinus/pulldown-cmark/releases/tag/v0.10.0> for more information.
   640→  [#2308](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2308)
   641→- The warning about the legacy `src/theme` directory has been removed.
   642→  [#2263](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2263)
   643→- Updated dependencies. MSRV raised to 1.71.0.
   644→  [#2283](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2283)
   645→  [#2293](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2293)
   646→  [#2297](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2297)
   647→  [#2310](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2310)
   648→  [#2309](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2309)
   649→- Some internal performance/memory improvements.
   650→  [#2273](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2273)
   651→  [#2290](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2290)
   652→- Made the `pathdiff` dependency optional based on the `watch` feature.
   653→  [#2291](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2291)
   655→### Fixed
   656→- The `s` shortcut key handler should not trigger when focus is in an HTML form.
   657→  [#2311](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2311)
   659→## mdBook 0.4.36
   660→[v0.4.35...v0.4.36](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/compare/v0.4.35...v0.4.36)
   662→### Added
   663→- Added Nim to the default highlighted languages.
   664→  [#2232](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/2232)
   665→- Added a small indicator for the sidebar resize handle.
