  1143→- Handle UTF-8 BOM for chapter sources.
  1144→  [#1285](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/1285)
  1145→- Removed extra whitespace added to `{{#playground}}` snippets.
  1146→  [#1375](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/1375)
