  1353→  [#1099](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/1099)
  1355→### Changed
  1356→- Use a different color for Ayu theme's highlighting for Rust attributes (uses
  1357→  a bright color instead of the comment color).
  1358→  [#1133](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/1133)
  1359→- Adjusted spacing of sidebar entries.
  1360→  [#1137](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/1137)
  1361→- Slightly adjusted line-height of `<p>`, `<ul>`, and `<ol>`.
  1362→  [#1136](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/1136)
  1363→- Handlebars updated to 3.0.
  1364→  [#1130](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/1130)
  1366→### Fixed
  1367→- Fix an issue with sidebar scroll position on reload.
  1368→  [#1108](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/1108)
  1369→- `mdbook serve` will retain the current scroll position when the page is reloaded.
  1370→  [#1097](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/1097)
  1371→- Fixed the page name if the book didn't have a title to not be prefixed with ` - `.
  1372→  [#1145](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/1145)
  1373→- HTML attributes `rel=next` and `rel=previous` are now supported in "wide"
  1374→  mode (previously they were only set in narrow mode).
  1375→  [#1150](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/1150)
  1376→- Prevent recursive copies when the destination directory is contained in the
  1377→  source directory.
  1378→  [#1135](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/1135)
  1379→- Adjusted the menu bar animation to not immediately obscure the top content.
  1380→  [#989](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/989)
  1381→- Fix for comments in SUMMARY.md that appear between items.
  1382→  [#1167](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pull/1167)
  1384→## mdBook 0.3.5
  1385→[6e0d0fa...efdb832](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/compare/6e0d0fa...efdb832)
