   347→    /// The logic for determining where a backend should put its build
   348→    /// artefacts.
   349→    ///
   350→    /// If there is only 1 renderer, put it in the directory pointed to by the
   351→    /// `build.build_dir` key in [`Config`]. If there is more than one then the
   352→    /// renderer gets its own directory within the main build dir.
   353→    ///
   354→    /// i.e. If there were only one renderer (in this case, the HTML renderer):
   355→    ///
   356→    /// - build/
   357→    ///   - index.html
   358→    ///   - ...
   359→    ///
   360→    /// Otherwise if there are multiple:
   361→    ///
   362→    /// - build/
   363→    ///   - epub/
   364→    ///     - my_awesome_book.epub
   365→    ///   - html/
   366→    ///     - index.html
   367→    ///     - ...
